title: Friday Night Funkin' - M.I.L.F but everytime it's Boyfriend turn a Different Skin Mod is used
author: PrizMatex
description:
My most favorite song in Friday Night Funkin and I was extremely happy to make this video. There aren't as many unique mom skins out there which is why the skins don't change per turn and also looking at my previous video I felt kinda bad that we barely got to witness some gameplay from some of them. Once again I still want people to know that I did use a bot to keep things well sync because I don't intend on hiding that fact since I wanted to make this video as a fun viewing experience while delivering people exposure of new skin mods out there. I guess M.I.L.F was a little harder to handle since there a were a few missed notes but I'm okay with that since it doesn't break the flow of music. That Lady Dimitrescu mod was my personal favorite that I gave her the best part of the song. Overall this was extremely fun and I do love how unique each art style are on the mom.
